Aamir Khan’s Dangal daughter Sanya Malhotra turns choreographer for him in Secret Superstar 
19-3-2017 
Bollywood actor Sanya Malhotra, who made her acting debut with Dangal alongside Aamir Khan,has now made Aamir dance on her finger tips.

Read more

Sanya choreographed a song for Aamir’s next, Secret Superstar. Sources close to Sanya claimed the steps were quite difficult but Aamir nailed it.

When asked about her experience, Sanya said, “The fact that I love to dance and love everything associated with it has never been a secret.When Advait asked me to choreograph a sequence for Aamir sir in Secret Superstar, I was ecstatic. Not in my wildest dreams could I have imagined doing something so wonderful.”

